cast.overview: A boy growing up in Dublin during the 1980s escapes his strained family life by starting a band to impress the mysterious girl he likes.
cast.title: Sing Street

details.biography: Chosen from an open casting for the leading role in Lance Daly's award winning feature Life's A Breeze, Kelly was nominated for a Lead Actress Film IFTA Award in 2014. Since then Kelly has been cast in a guest lead in RTE's most successful TV drama, Love Hate and appeared in season four of the show in the Autumn of 2013. Kelly appeared in John Carney's feature film Sing Street opposite Aidan Gillen and Jack Reynor.
details.name: Kelly Thornton
